<li class='cover' id='bookCover_240373'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/240373.The_Children_s_Blizzard"><img alt="The Children&#39;s Blizzard" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1407706474l/240373._SX98_.jpg" />
