<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/53121652-a-furious-sky"><img alt="A Furious Sky: The Five-Hundred-Year History of America&#39;s Hurricanes" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1571125597l/53121652._SX98_SY160_.jpg" />
