<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/49376.Rising_Tide"><img alt="Rising Tide: The Great Mississippi Flood of 1927 and How It Changed America" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1442853802l/49376._SX98_.jpg" />
